io.mosip.registration.service.sync

  • Packages that use io.mosip.registration.service.sync 
    Package Description
    io.mosip.registration.service.packet.impl  
    io.mosip.registration.service.sync.impl  
  • Classes in io.mosip.registration.service.sync used by io.mosip.registration.service.packet.impl 
    Class and Description
    PacketSynchService
    This class invokes the external MOSIP service 'Packet Sync' to sync the packet ids, which are ready for upload to the server from client.
  • Classes in io.mosip.registration.service.sync used by io.mosip.registration.service.sync.impl 
    Class and Description
    MasterSyncService
    It makes call to the external 'MASTER Sync' services to download the master data which are relevant to center specific by passing the center id or mac address or machine id.
    PolicySyncService
    It provides the method to download the Mosip public key specific to the user's local machines and center specific and store the same into local db for further usage during registration process.
    PreRegistrationDataSyncService
    It interfaces with external pre-registration data sync services and download the packets based on the date range and packet id then store it into the local machine in encrypted format.
    PublicKeySync
    It downloads the Mosip public key from server and store the same into local database for further usage.
    SyncStatusValidatorService
    RegistrationApprovalService is the registration approval service Interface
    TPMPublicKeySyncService
    Service interface to sync the TPM public key with the server
